## CORRECT INSTALLATION COMMANDS

### ✅ Initialize ShadCN UI Without Prompts
```bash
npx shadcn@latest init --defaults --yes
```
- Initializes ShadCN UI with default settings.
- Skips prompts for style and color selection.
